<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07952</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE MODERNIZATION OF THE PHILIPPINE NUCLEAR RESEARCH INSTITUTE, DEPARTMENT OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY (PNRI-DOST), AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT :  Mandates the PNRI to be the only government agency to promote the peaceful applications of nuclear and radiation science and technology to be a center of excellence for nuclear and radiation science and technology. Provides for the acquisition and upgrade of PNRI’s instruments, equipment and facilities and to phase out obsolete ones.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Philippine Atomic Energy Research Institute of the Department of Science and Technology (PNRI-DOS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>MANGAOANG, ALLEN JESSE C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-07-24</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-16)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY ON 2018-08-01</td></tr></table>